      <section eId="sec_8203">
        <num>8203</num>
        <heading>Amount of costs on appeal to appellate division and appellate term</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_8203__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Unless the court awards a lesser amount, costs awarded on an\nappeal to the appellate division shall be in the amount of two hundred\nfifty dollars.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_8203__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Costs on an appeal from a county court to an appellate term may be\nawarded by the appellate term in its discretion, and if awarded shall be\nas follows:\n  1. to the appellant upon reversal, not more than thirty dollars;\n  2. to the respondent upon affirmance, not more than twenty-five\ndollars;\n  3. to either party on modification, not more than twenty-five dollars.\n  On appeal from any other court to an appellate term costs shall be\ngoverned by the provisions of the applicable court act.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
